{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/seniors/journeys-tests-or-doctor","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"Journeys to tests or doctor","meta_description":"Call your doctor first and consult with them, if you must come in person.\r\n\r\n\r\n","content":{"processed":"<h2>Recommendations</h2>\n<p><strong>Call your doctor first </strong>and consult<strong> </strong>with them, if it is necessary for you to come in person. If you need to see a doctor in person. Try to avoid places with an increased risk of infection.</p>\n<p>If possible, travel by car or call a taxi. Only stay in the waiting room for the necessary time and keep the distances between other patients.</p>\n<p>Of course, cover your mouth and nose with a face mask. Avoid touching objects that have been touched by patients before you (such as handles, railings).</p>\n<p>However, do not underestimate the importance of <strong>preventive health checkups!</strong></p>\n<h2> </h2>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/seniors/journeys-tests-or-doctor"},"changed":"2020-11-10T22:12:35+00:00","valid_from":null,"langcode":"en","created":"2020-11-07T17:28:47+00:00","links":[{"uri":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=daWguhKJ1Qg","title":"Jak postupovat při návštěvě lékaře?"}],"relationships":{"region":[{"name":"All regions of Czechia"}],"icon":null,"situation_type":{"name":"Seniors","path":{"alias":"/situations/seniors"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"elderly"}}},"measures":[],"related_situations":[{"title":"How to get tested?","path":{"alias":"/situations/infection-and-general-measures/how-get-tested","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Types of protection","path":{"alias":"/situations/face-masks/types-protection","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"What is the purpose of face masks and respirators?","path":{"alias":"/situations/face-masks-and-respirators/what-purpose-face-masks-and-respirators","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Hand washing","path":{"alias":"/situations/hygiene/hand-wa